```plantuml
@startuml Spiderpig86_SmoresUnderflow

actor User
participant "su-frontend" as Frontend
participant "su-users" as UsersService
participant "su-accounts" as AccountsService
participant "su-questions" as QuestionsService
participant "su-answers" as AnswersService
participant "su-search" as SearchService
participant "su-media" as MediaService
participant "RabbitMQ" as RabbitMQ
participant "qu-questions" as QueueQuestions
participant "qu-answers" as QueueAnswers
participant "qu-delete-questions" as QueueDeleteQuestions
participant "ElasticSearch" as ElasticSearch
participant "MongoDB" as MongoDB
participant "Redis" as Redis

User -> Frontend: Access Application
Frontend -> UsersService: Authenticate User
UsersService -> AccountsService: Verify Account
AccountsService --> UsersService: Account Verified
UsersService --> Frontend: JWT Token

User -> Frontend: Post Question
Frontend -> QuestionsService: Submit Question
QuestionsService -> RabbitMQ: Queue Question
RabbitMQ -> QueueQuestions: Process Question
QueueQuestions -> MongoDB: Store Question
QueueQuestions -> ElasticSearch: Index Question

User -> Frontend: Post Answer
Frontend -> AnswersService: Submit Answer
AnswersService -> RabbitMQ: Queue Answer
RabbitMQ -> QueueAnswers: Process Answer
QueueAnswers -> MongoDB: Store Answer
QueueAnswers -> ElasticSearch: Index Answer

User -> Frontend: Search for Questions
Frontend -> SearchService: Request Search
SearchService -> ElasticSearch: Fetch Results
ElasticSearch --> SearchService: Return Results
SearchService --> Frontend: Display Results

User -> Frontend: Upload Media
Frontend -> MediaService: Upload Request
MediaService -> MongoDB: Store Media Metadata

@enduml
```